1. nh ngha vn (Define Problem)

M t:

B d liu v bnh i tho ng Pima Indian (Pima Indians Diabetes Dataset) c thu thp t cng ng ngi da  Pima.

D liu ny bao gm nhiu c im lm sng v nhn khu hc ca bnh nhn.

Mc tiu l d on kh nng mc bnh tiu ng (diabetes) ca mt c nhn da trn cc thng tin y t c bn.

  • D liu vo (Input features):

    • S ln mang thai (Pregnancies)

    • Nng glucose huyt tng sau 2 gi (Glucose)

    • Huyt p tm trng (BloodPressure)

    • dy np gp da (SkinThickness)

    • Nng insulin (Insulin)

    • s khi c th (BMI)

    • chc nng ph h tiu ng (DiabetesPedigreeFunction)

    • Tui (Age)

  • Kt qu (Output):

    • Outcome (0 = Khng mc bnh, 1 = Mc bnh)

(5) Mi tng quan gia cc tnh cht (Correlations)

S tng quan (correlation) cp n mi quan h gia hai bin v cch chng c th c hoc khng cng nhau thay i.

Phng php ph bin nht tnh ton tng quan l Pearson's Correlation Coeficient, gi nh c mt phn phi chun ca cc thuc tnh lin quan. Tng quan -1 hoc 1 cho thy mi tng quan m hoc dng y tng ng. Trong khi gi tr 0 hin th khng tng quan tt c.

$$ r = \frac{\sum_{i=1}^n{\left(x_i - \hat{x}\right)\left(y_i - \hat{y}\right)}}{\sqrt{\sum_{i=1}^n{\left(x_i - \hat{x}\right)^2}\sum_{i=1}^n{\left(y_i - \hat{y}\right)^2}}} $$

Mt s thut ton hc my nh hi quy tuyn tnh v logistic c hiu sut km nu c cc thuc tnh tng quan cao trong tp d liu ca bn.

Nh vy, tht s cn thit xem xt tt c cc mi tng quan theo cp ca cc thuc tnh trong tp d liu.

(1) Hin th trn tng tnh cht n

Biu hp v ru

https://www.simplypsychology.org/boxplots.html

  • So snh cc trung v (median) tng ng ca mi hp (box plot). Nu ng trung v ca mt hp nm bn ngoi ca mt hp so snh, th c th c s khc bit gia hai nhm.
  • So snh chiu di hp kim tra cch d liu c phn tn gia mi mu. Hp cng di th d liu cng phn tn. D liu cng nh cng t b phn tn.
  • Mt ngoi l (outlier) c nh ngha l mt im d liu nm bn ngoi phn ra (whiskers) ca hp.
  • Kim tra hng lch ca d liu (cn i, cc phn t tp trung tri, phi).
    • Median gia hp v ru (whiskers) hai bn nh nhau th phn b l i xng.
    • Median gn y hp hn v nu ru ngn hn u di ca hp, th phn phi l lch dng (lch phi).
    • Median gn u hp hn v nu ru ngn hn u trn ca hp, th phn b b lch m (lch tri
In[10]:
# Xc nh cc ct cn x l nhiu
cols_with_outliers = ['SkinThickness', 'Insulin', 'Pregnancies']

# Lp qua cc ct  gii hn gi tr nhiu bng IQR
for col in cols_with_outliers:
    Q1 = df[col].quantile(0.25)
    Q3 = df[col].quantile(0.75)
    IQR = Q3 - Q1
    
    # Tnh gii hn trn v di
    lower_bound = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR
    upper_bound = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
    
    # Gii hn cc gi tr nm ngoi phm vi
    df[col] = np.where(df[col] < lower_bound, lower_bound, df[col])
    df[col] = np.where(df[col] > upper_bound, upper_bound, df[col])

print(" gii hn Outliers bng phng php IQR.")

 gii hn Outliers bng phng php IQR.

Kt qu nh gi cho thy m hnh K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) ca bn t chnh xc kh tt (77.27%), nhng n ang mc phi mt li nghim trng i vi bi ton y t:

  • M hnh qu t trong vic xc nh ngi mc bnh.

  • Ch s Recall ( nhy) cho lp Mc bnh (1) ch t 44%. iu ny c ngha l m hnh b st 56% s ngi thc s mc bnh (31 ngi).

  • Li False Negative (31 ngi) ny l ri ro cao nht, v n c th khin bnh nhn thc s mc bnh b chn on l khe mnh.

Tm li: M hnh hin ti khng ng tin cy cho vic chn on v n qu thin v lp ngi khe mnh v b st qu nhiu ca mc bnh. Bn cn iu chnh m hnh (v d: dng SMOTE, thay i K, hoc i thut ton) tng Recall cho lp mc bnh

(3) Chun ha d liu (Data Normalize)

Chun ha cc tnh cht a v cng mt min tr

  • Min-Max Normalization $$ z = \frac{x - min(x)}{max(x) - min(x)} $$
  • Standard Normalization $$ z = \frac{x - \mu}{\sigma} $$

Lu : Qu trnh chun ha c th lm trong phn thc nghim thut ton

In[43]:
